            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-mint-400">IRA treatment expected (favorable)</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-red-400">Student asset — up to 20% assessed/yr</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white">Best for</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">Free money + long-term growth</td>
